    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I'm parting with my car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can definitely count on it for everything from your daily commute to fun weekend road trips. It runs smoothly, looks great, and is just waiting for a new home. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
