    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for peak volumetric efficiency. The drivetrain consists of a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, addressing common E46 weak points. The chassis is dialed in with upgraded bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining excellent lateral stiffness. A mechanically robust driver's car with a clean title and documented service history.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
