    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example that balances performance with everyday usability. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with regular driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the bolsters on the driver's seat show light entry wear, but the leather remains soft with no tears. All digital displays and climate controls are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is robust, featuring a documented service history including a recent oil service and a fresh set of tires. It starts promptly, idles smoothly, and the transmission shifts through all gears without hesitation. This is a solid, reliable driver\u2019s car that has been cared for by an enthusiast.",
