      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit has been meticulously maintained with a focus on preventative structural and mechanical integrity: the rear subframe has been reinforced with TMS plates, and the VANOS system was overhauled using Beisan Systems components to ensure optimal cam timing. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission shifts precisely, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight. The suspension utilizes refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers for maintained kinematic accuracy. While the finish shows minor road patina consistent with its mileage, the engine exhibits excellent compression and peak volumetric efficiency. This is a driver-focused example where mechanical performance and chassis rigidity take priority.",
